    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370220/extras/d170046861fcc01dc3c87803e6ceaceb.avif?t=1739792796\" width=600 height=125 /></span><br><br>Smells Like Burnt Rubber直观的游戏玩法不需要玩家学习大量的操作。立即进入游戏！游戏完全支持手柄操作。<br>利用周末时间互相碰撞。忘记周围的世界。忽略您所爱的人。您再也不会使用自己的汽车了--卖掉它，买这款游戏（两次）！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370220/extras/55c76ced46c8d81ca19bae8f127ec6c9.poster.avif?t=1739792796\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370220/extras/55c76ced46c8d81ca19bae8f127ec6c9.webm?t=1739792796\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370220/extras/55c76ced46c8d81ca19bae8f127ec6c9.mp4?t=1739792796\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在线多人游戏</h2>参加与全球其他玩家的在线比赛。您也可以通过在线合作，与本地玩家或朋友一起游戏。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >最多4人分屏</h2><br>通过分屏与您的朋友在沙发上合作比赛，无论是几场比赛还是完整的大奖赛体验。在您驶向终点线的同时，与您的朋友进行倒车比赛，看着他们在您面前爆炸。<br><br>(对于本地多人游戏，您可以使用一个键盘和任意数量的游戏手柄)<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370220/extras/599173694a9aa643e313fa35437d587e.poster.avif?t=1739792796\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370220/extras/599173694a9aa643e313fa35437d587e.webm?t=1739792796\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370220/extras/599173694a9aa643e313fa35437d587e.mp4?t=1739792796\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >赛道</h2><br>在水泥赛道上与跑车比赛。在泥泞的赛道上，用您的怪兽卡车将其他车手推入防撞栏。但是要小心！有些轨道可能会给您带来惊喜。所以最好小心火车。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370220/extras/060ca8d2f41959797bfb0cfc71a8896b.avif?t=1739792796\" width=616 height=230 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >车辆组</h2><br>为轨道选择不同的车辆组将重新洗牌。它完全改变了您的转弯和寻求与他人碰撞的方式。您需要采取相应的策略才能获胜。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370220/extras/934cdfcfad9715bdd42719971034dba3.poster.avif?t=1739792796\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370220/extras/934cdfcfad9715bdd42719971034dba3.webm?t=1739792796\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩家定制和车辆改装</h2><br>用不同颜色的套装装扮您的头像。更多自定义选项包括玩家图标和旗帜。创建一个让您的朋友（或敌人）感到恐惧的形象。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370220/extras/1c44e73738e9f56125bbdbed8fd3d4b9.poster.avif?t=1739792796\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370220/extras/1c44e73738e9f56125bbdbed8fd3d4b9.webm?t=1739792796\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370220/extras/1c44e73738e9f56125bbdbed8fd3d4b9.mp4?t=1739792796\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在游戏过程中，您将获得名声，从而解锁新的改装部件。您可以获得新的轮胎来改变在不同路面上的抓地力，或者为您的自行车添加芯片调校。<br>您还可以选择使用丰富多彩的车身底部照明来进一步定制您的车辆。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370220/extras/e404a87a332f6e5216c8c763dbbaaf32.poster.avif?t=1739792796\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370220/extras/e404a87a332f6e5216c8c763dbbaaf32.webm?t=1739792796\" type=\"video/webm;